								<p class="label">Blog Post</p>
								<h3 class="title"><a id="bottom_0_ctl00_rptOuterPcp_rptInnerPcp_0_hlArticleTitle_3" data-loc="loc:body" href="/blogs/up-front/posts/2013/03/07-education-goal-post-2015-anderson">Toward Consensus on a Goal for Education within the Post-2015 Development Agenda: A Tale of Two Regional Consultations</a></h3>
